{"tid":943784,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌！無幫老婆交電話費，再比佢串我唔識英文","createTime":"2018-12-16T17:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T19:42:20.000Z","uid":17896,"like":8,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c88780bb8f1f283db3e463d3438f4fa66ba830","tid":943784,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:06:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的！話說我唔記得幫老婆交電話費，佢係咁屌柒我，又話我英文都唔識多個，點知比我串返佢唔撚柒識中文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：老婆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：叫左你幫我交電話費，日撚日都話攰唔記得左交，打電話提你又話附近無CSL ,獲撚獲你都有藉口......（講左一輪咀我都唔知佢講左乜鳩）<br />\n<br />\n返工已經受氣，收工緊係打機輕鬆下，我就一句屌埋去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咪撚嘈撚住我打機啦！屌！！！<br />\n<br />\n佢又唔洗返工，日日係屋企打機上網我都唔撚理，直到佢講左一句我成個人跳撚左制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：無撚用呀你！嫁左比你叫你做小小時都做唔到，CLS!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你講乜野，講還講唔好講英文，咩叫CLS<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我話CLS 呀 痴撚線呀，中文呀，明唔明呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我呢刻比佢搞到無地自容，才生急智，戶口得返三個九毫七，銀包得返五舊水，我就話喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你咁撚得閒自己去我銀包拎五舊去 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">痴線撚</span> 交電話費啦！！！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你係咪打機打到傻左呀，咩痴線撚呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：痴線撚呀！中文呀，CSL呀，識唔撚識呀！今晚出廳訓，咪撚嘈住我打機！<br />\n<br />\n件事就咁完左，佢無理我三日，都唔係問題，因為成日都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係有無巴打借幾舊比我過埋今個月，得返三個九毫七食飯都無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"03b7a6300135e30fb481c4e9cc487bdbeb844113","tid":943784,"uid":33533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"一般般"},{"pid":"4cde6ebddae0a135b4391ac99092999ac89f01fc","tid":943784,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"拍拍"},{"pid":"d55ad3a80fdbe7ff65d6059a64ff065e74e936e9","tid":943784,"uid":205420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:08:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚線夫妻...."},{"pid":"93f7ff438c5070ca452042fc53ed73ed2b90b8ab","tid":943784,"uid":92,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c3/026andy_lau_crazy.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091215094325\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc3%2F026andy_lau_crazy.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20091215094325&h=890ac917&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9250ea76c6cfd5c73c4bc499cf3d2bfa67fea4d8","tid":943784,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:09:47.000Z","msg":"OK<br />\n60/100"},{"pid":"6728a7b6e0952717f0e3a467622c0231755d0284","tid":943784,"uid":56999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"英文叻又點<br />\n咪又係要訓低比你屌"},{"pid":"255f6c3cd3d00d60ae6b8d6f67e97df3e232165c","tid":943784,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"戶口號碼??聽日返工順路過比你"},{"pid":"ce33ff8c180b8afd35f9b23e0d92910a94e99191","tid":943784,"uid":440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"1/10 勇氣可嘉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"